355
00:20:46,165 --> 00:20:48,333
On est des voyageurs !
Pas vrai ?

356
00:20:52,080 --> 00:20:53,857
Me forcez pas à chanter !

357
00:20:54,567 --> 00:20:55,462
Allez.

358
00:20:55,958 --> 00:20:58,176
<i>Busted flat in Baton Rouge</i>

359
00:20:58,336 --> 00:21:03,015
