379
00:22:03,235 --> 00:22:04,785
- Tes clés.
- Quoi ?

380
00:22:04,945 --> 00:22:06,613
Tes clés de bagnole, maintenant.

381
00:22:07,280 --> 00:22:08,545
Attends, je...

