00:22:11,952 --> 00:22:13,126
Tu les as perdues ?

384
00:22:13,287 --> 00:22:14,787
Oh, non. Merde.

385
00:22:15,372 --> 00:22:16,625
Merde. C'est...

386
00:22:20,282 --> 00:22:23,136
- Non, ce n'est...
