412
00:23:51,680 --> 00:23:52,726
C'est quoi ?

413
00:23:54,039 --> 00:23:55,062
Quoi ?

414
00:23:55,758 --> 00:23:57,022
Ce bruit...

415
00:23:57,182 --> 00:23:58,523
